T1  - How are shorts informed?: Short sellers, news, and information processing
AU  - Engelberg, Joseph E.
AU  - Reed, Adam V.
AU  - Ringgenberg, Matthew C.
JO  - Journal of Financial Economics
VL  - 105
IS  - 2
SP  - 260
EP  - 278
